 candidates court Iowa farmers by blasting US-China trade war"></picture></a></div><div class="info"><h5 class="title"><a href="https://www.foxnews.com/politics/2020-presidential-candidates-court-iowa-farmers-by-blasting-us-china-trade-war">2020 presidential candidates court Iowa farmers by blasting US-China trade war</a></h5><div class="meta"><!----><!----></div></div></article></li><li><article class="article"><div class="m"><a href="https://www.foxnews.com/politics/cohen-adds-2-new-lawyers-to-legal-team-as-he-prepares-fr-congressional-testimonies"><picture><img src="https://a57.foxnews.com/media2.foxnews.com/BrightCove/694940094001/2019/01/23/270/152/694940094001_5992993978001_5992990247001-vs.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1" alt="Date set for Cohen to testify before House Intel Committee, as 2 new lawyers join his legal team"></picture></a></div><div class="info"><h5 class="title"><a href="https://www.foxnews.com/politics/cohen-adds-2-new-lawyers-to-legal-team-as-he-prepares-fr-congressional-testimonies">Date set for Cohen to testify before House Intel Committee, as 2 new lawyers join his legal team</a></h5><div class="meta"><!----><!----></div></div></article></li></ul></div><!----></section><div class="ad-container desktop"><div data-ad-pos="desktop" data-ad-size="300x251" data-ad-lz="" class="ad gpt "></div><span class="advert-txt">ADVERTISEMENT</span></div><div data-uid="ar-11" class="vendor-unit"></div></div></div></aside></div></article></main></div><div class="post-content"></div></div><footer class="site-footer"><div class="footer-upper"><div class="section-nav"><div class="inner"><nav><h6 class="nav-title"><a href="/us">U.S.</a></h6><ul><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/crime">Crime</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/military">Military</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/education">Education</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/terror">Terror</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/immigration">Immigrat